These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: sprite, almond-milk
Movie-Genre: epic, action
Sport: parkour, lacrosse
Transport: trike, roller
1. Transport:roller is on the left or right of Sport:lacrosse##3
2. Beverage:almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:action == Beverage:sprite##1
4. Transport:roller is on the right of Transport:trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | sprite  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | epic   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour |
| Transport     | trike | roller    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: lemon, banana
Movie-Genre: satire, sports
Pet: bird, mouse
Transport: helicopter, taxi
1. Pet:mouse is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:satire == Transport:taxi##1
3. Food:banana is on the right of Movie-Genre:sports##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | lemon     | banana |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire  |
| Pet           | mouse         | bird     |
| Transport     | helicopter   | taxi    |

 #################################
 
