Nationality: french, pakistani
Pet: goldfish, goat
Sport: baseball, ice-hockey
1. Sport:ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:journalist == Nationality:french##1
4. Pet:goldfish is on the left of Nationality:pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | journalist | photographer    |
| Nationality   | french       | pakistani |
| Pet           | goldfish         | goat    |
| Sport         | baseball    | ice-hockey   |

